title: Maldives GDP From Transport
description: GDP from Transport in Maldives increased to 3437.50 MVR Million in 2021 from 2308.90 MVR Million in 2020. GDP from Transport in Maldives averaged 2822.66 MVR Million from 2003 until 2021, reaching an all time high of 4330.50 MVR Million in 2019 and a record low of 1310 MVR Million in 2003. This page provides - Maldives Gdp From Transport- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Maldives Monetary Authority
